            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex cert="low">extus</ex></expan> Vibius Valen<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied> <lb n="3"/>immere<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> hic o<supplied reason="lost">c</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>cisus sum una cum <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erio</ex></expan> Ingenuo adfi<lb break="no" n="6"/>ne meo sine ullo <lb n="7"/>praemio et sine ul<lb break="no" n="8"/>la ira <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>nnos</ex></expan> XXVIII <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>gratul</abbr><ex>or</ex></expan> pare<supplied reason="lost">nti</supplied> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostro</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/>qui bono praeside <lb n="11"/>sanguen <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostrum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>vindik</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan> <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex cert="low">extus</ex></expan> Vibius Secundinus <lb n="13"/>fratri piissimo <expan><abbr>po</abbr><ex>suit</ex></expan> t<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>t</abbr><ex>u</ex><abbr>l</abbr></expan>(um)
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 2 u. 12: möglicherweise S mit nur aufgemalter Querhaste für S(extus); eventuell auch S(purius). Z. 13: po(suit) s(it) t(ibi) t(erra) l(evis) ebenfalls denkbar. (B): Beševliev; AE 1957: Abweichungen in Lesung / Ergänzung.</p>
            </div>
